column5: My friends dad bought a place on White lake just south of Bob's lake in Frontenac county. Not to be confused with the white lake about 10km away northwest of Bob.  We have no idea whats in their waiting to be caught? Anyone know? Or where i can find out?  -Dave
there should be water....  Sorry couldnt resist ( i tried too )

It's not lake on the edge of the park. It's south of bob's lake beside potspoon. I know what other lakes have in the area, and i was just wondering if any one had any info specifically about that lake.  -R-
